name: Qmem - Aku Lagi Marah! Tolong Ngerti, OK???
description:
"Aku lagi marah! Tolong ngerti, OK???"

is a song about a man that have silent treatment from his partner, He is definitely very sad, because he is mad and mental. Because his partner never with him, every time he want to cry. because he doesn't know, because he doesn't have a partner actually. His mental breakdown, crying in the edge of the well, My darling, Farewell!
